nl.weeaboo.vn.save

Interface IStorage

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface IStorage
extends java.io.Serializable
    Provides general-purpose key/value storage. Storing null values isn't supported; any attempt to store a null value will instead remove any existing value stored under that key.

    Supported data types:

    • boolean
    • double
    • string

    All numeric values are stored as double-precision floating point values internally.
